parameters:
Memimi: Ugh... why... whyyyy... this is... *sob*...
*sniffle*...

Male Student: Negotiating with the entire student body is
hard labor, there's no way I'd do it for free, right? Help
me post it on SNS. Oh, should we make it a game?

Male Student: From here, if you can walk around the
schoolyard while peeing without stopping, I'll make sure no
one at school can order you around. How about it?... Well,
it's not like you have a choice, it's an order, so you have
to do it.

Memimi: Something like that...! That's awful... in the
schoolyard... everyone's watching... ahhhh... *sob*... I
can't... *sob*...

Memimi found herself forced into the most degrading game
imaginable: if she could make a naked lap around the
schoolyard while urinating, she would be exempt from being
ordered around...

Memimi: *hic*... ugh, ughhh...! It's embarrassing... such a
distance... *groan*... absolutely impossible... *sob*...
there's no way I can do it... waaaahhh...!

Male Student: You won't know unless you try, right, Shark
Mountain-san? If you succeed, a rosy school life awaits you!
And if you fail, nothing changes, so it's a win-win!

Memimi: Doing something like this is a loss from the
start... ughhh, it's too cruel... *hic*... *sob*...

No matter how much Memimi cried or screamed, it was decided
that she would pee here. Trying to cling to a one in ten
thousand chance, she tensed her lower abdomen...

Memimi: (If it's come to this, I have to succeed at all
costs...! If my pee can last for 30 seconds... how many
meters is the schoolyard? If I dash...)

Male Student: Whoa, she's really peeing!! Isn't it bad for
the student council president to pee in the schoolyard?
You're being filmed, you know~?

Male Student: Gahaha, if it stops even once, that's the end
of it, you know? But if you let it all out at once, it'll be
over quickly too... You have to adjust the flow just right~

Memimi: *panting*... I have to run faster...! There's no
time...

Female Student: Eww, it's splashing!! President, you clean
that up yourself, please! Ugh, it's disgusting...

Male Student: Are you going to make it at that pace~? Ahaha,
running with a wide stance while peeing... I've never seen
such a pathetic girl!

Memimi: Waaahhhhhnnn... don't look at meee... I can't bear
it... don't look... *sob*... waaah, ahhh...

Male Student: The student council president peeing standing
up is rare~ I've seen her having sex all over the net! It
actually smells like pee here~. It's gross but if it's
Memimi-president's, I'm totally fine with it!

Male Student: You still have a long way to go, president~.
Better hurry up? Running while spraying pee everywhere, how
pitiful!

Memimi: *hic*... ughh"... *sob*... everyone's..." laughing
at me"... ugh... ugh"...! I can't do this anymore...
ughh...! Ughh...

Male Student: Oh no, you're losing momentum, president!!
You've barely started running!! You won't make it around the
schoolyard at this rate!!

Male Student: This is no time to stop! Do you want to lose
the game?! Everyone will give you terrible orders~?

Memimi: I can't anymore... *sniffle*... can't run anymore...
it's impossibleee... *sob*... please forgive me"... *groan*,
ughh, eehh...

Memimi's legs were shaking so much that she could no longer
even walk. Eventually her urination stopped and instead a
large amount of tears and snot began to drip down towards
the ground.

Frustration, embarrassment, helplessness, defeat... The
emotions enveloping her were a jumbled mess that could no
longer be put into words. Amidst the laughter, Memimi
continued to cry endlessly...
